				</video>
				<button id="csbtn" onclick="csclick();"><i class="fa fa-pause" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>

				<p>Nearby, they find a wall-mounted touchscreen - locked down to display the <span class="spanTech spanHTML">HTML</span> page below.<p>
				<img class="projectImg" src="/img/butterflypainter.jpg">
				<p>The visitor is able to 'finger paint' onto a cutout representation of a butterfly's wing, using basic paint controls and colour-picking palettes.</p>
				<p>When they are done, they hit a 'finish' button to see the butterfly they have just designed fly into the scene being projected onto the wall.</p>



				<p>The site was built on <span class="spanTech spanNode">Node</span> and <span class="spanTech spanFramework">Express</span> foundations, using <span class="spanTech spanJavascript">jQuery</span>, <span class="spanTech spanCSS">Bootstrap</span> and <span class="spanTech spanJavascript">Masonry</span> on the front-end.
